text: August Strindberg (1849–1912), was a Swedish dramatist and painter. Strindberg may also refer to: ==People== * Nils Strindberg (1872–1897), Swedish photographer * Anita Strindberg (born 1937), Swedish actor * Henrik Strindberg (born 1954), Swedish composer ==Other== * Strindberg Museum, Stockholm, Sweden * Strindberg (crater), an impact basin in the Shakespeare quadrangle of Mercury
